Quiqr is an open source project and we strive to form an healty, open and inspiring community. For everyone who likes to give a positive contribution&hellip; feel welcome!
We are organized on GitHub and currently our main projects are&hellip;
Quiqr Desktop - The Quiqr Desktop Application project, Quiqr Desktop is currently powered by ElectronJS Quiqr Community Templates - Community driven list of Hugo site templates with a Quiqr Content Model The Quiqr Book - The Quiqr documentation project for users and developers Embgit - Quiqr&rsquo;s integrated Git Client written in Go.
